item.title: About
item.description: About Me Hello! I’m xtcel, a seasoned software engineer with over a decade of experience in the tech industry. I graduated from Fujian Normal University with a degree in Software Engineering, and since then, I’ve been passionately involved in the world of internet product development. Professional Journey With 10 years of hands-on experience in internet product development, I’ve honed my skills across a wide array of technologies. My expertise spans multiple platforms and frameworks, allowing me to create versatile and robust solutions.
